## 🔍 Troubleshooting

### Common Issues

*Q: Exercises not loading?*
A: Ensure you're running the application from a web server (not file:// protocol) or use the manual file loading feature.

*Q: Progress not saving?*
A: Check that your browser allows local storage and isn't in private/incognito mode.

*Q: Mobile display issues?*
A: Clear your browser cache and ensure you're using a supported browser version.

*Q: Vocabulary search not working?*
A: Refresh the page and try again. Ensure JavaScript is enabled in your browser.

